                        <div class="fb-page" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/Chánh-Thu-Store-100075403785205/" data-tabs="events,messages" data-width="500" data-height="270" data-small-header="true" data-adapt-container-width="true" data-hide-cover="false" data-show-facepile="true"><blockquote cite="https://www.facebook.com/XBOX-Vietnam-100734395082213/" class="fb-xfbml-parse-ignore"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/XBOX-Vietnam-100734395082213/">XBOX Vietnam</a></blockquote></div>
